'''1977年俄国流感'''（英文：'''1977 Russian flu'''）是指最早由[[苏联|苏联]]于1977年报告的[[流感大流行|流感大流行]]，疫情持续至1979年<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Influenza Pandemic Plan. The Role of WHO and Guidelines for National and Regional Planning|url=https://www.who.int/csr/resources/publications/influenza/whocdscsredc991.pdf|date=April 1999|publisher=[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]|pages=38, 41|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203084733/https://www.who.int/csr/resources/publications/influenza/whocdscsredc991.pdf|archivedate=2020-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Swine-origin influenza virus in young age groups|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(09)61145-4/abstract|last=Mermel|first=Leonard A.|date=2009-06-20|journal=The Lancet|issue=9681|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(09)61145-4|volume=373|pages=2108–2109|language=en|issn=0140-6736|pmid=19541030|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727045637/https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(09)61145-4/fulltext}}</ref>。1977年5月，[[中国北方与南方|中国北方]]的疫情稍早于苏联爆发<ref name=":12">{{Cite journal|title=中国流感大流行的百年历史|author=秦颖 等|url=http://html.rhhz.net/zhlxbx/20180803.htm|journal=《中华流行病学杂志》（''Chinese Journal of Epidemiology''）|issue=8|year=2018|volume=39|page=1028-1031|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109065742/http://html.rhhz.net/zhlxbx/20180803.htm|archivedate=2021-01-09|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=Influenza in China in 1977: recurrence of influenzavirus A subtype H1N1|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2395678/|last=Kung|first=H. C.|last2=Jen|first2=K. F.|date=1978|journal=Bulletin of the World Health Organization|issue=6|volume=56|pages=913–918|issn=0042-9686|pmc=2395678|pmid=310732|last3=Yuan|first3=W. C.|last4=Tien|first4=S. F.|last5=Chu|first5=C. M.|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119215524/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2395678/}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title=The Re-Emergence of H1N1 Influenza Virus in 1977: A Cautionary Tale for Estimating Divergence Times Using Biologically Unrealistic Sampling Dates|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2887442/|last=Wertheim|first=Joel O.|date=2010-06-17|journal=PLoS ONE|issue=6|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0011184|volume=5|issn=1932-6203|pmc=2887442|pmid=20567599|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309011111/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2887442/}}</ref>。此次大流行主要感染25岁或26岁及以下的人群<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":12" /><ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title=The Reemergent 1977 H1N1 Strain and the Gain-of-Function Debate|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4542197/|last=Rozo|first=Michelle|last2=Gronvall|first2=Gigi Kwik|date=2015-08-18|journal=mBio|issue=4|doi=10.1128/mBio.01013-15|volume=6|issn=2150-7511|pmc=4542197|pmid=26286690|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2022-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220103062440/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4542197/}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite journal|title=The Russian flu. Its history and implications for this year's influenza season|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/702749|last=Gregg|first=M. B.|last2=Hinman|first2=A. R.|date=1978-11-17|journal=JAMA|issue=21|doi=10.1001/jama.240.21.2260|volume=240|pages=2260–2263|issn=0098-7484|pmid=702749|last3=Craven|first3=R. B.|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129213311/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/702749/}}</ref>，在世界范围内造成了约70万人死亡<ref name=":6">{{Cite journal|title=Novel swine-origin influenza A virus in humans: another pandemic knocking at the door|author=|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00430-009-0118-5/tables/1|last=Michaelis|first=Martin|last2=Doerr|first2=Hans Wilhem|date=2009-08|journal=Medical Microbiology and Immunology|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s00430-009-0118-5|volume=198|pages=175–183|issn=1432-1831|pmid=19543913|last3=Cinatl|first3=Jindrich|access-date=2021-07-22|archive-date=2021-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515002754/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00430-009-0118-5/tables/1}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite journal|title=Reorganize and survive—a recommendation for healthcare services affected by COVID-19—the ophthalmology experience|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41433-020-0871-7|last=Petrovski|first=Beáta Éva|last2=Lumi|first2=Xhevat|date=2020-07|journal=Eye|issue=7|doi=10.1038/s41433-020-0871-7|volume=34|pages=1177–1179|language=en|issn=1476-5454|last3=Znaor|first3=Ljubo|last4=Ivastinović|first4=Domagoj|last5=Confalonieri|first5=Filippo|last6=Petrovič|first6=Mojca Globočnik|last7=Petrovski|first7=Goran|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117231630/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41433-020-0871-7}}</ref><ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=You're more likely to die from the H1N1 flu if you were born in 1957|url=https://nouvelles.umontreal.ca/en/article/2018/01/19/you-re-more-likely-to-die-from-the-h1n1-flu-if-you-were-born-in-1957/|date=2020-11-18|publisher=University of Montreal|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190131183201/https://nouvelles.umontreal.ca/en/article/2018/01/19/you-re-more-likely-to-die-from-the-h1n1-flu-if-you-were-born-in-1957/|archivedate=2019-01-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该疫情由[[H1N1流感病毒|H1N1流感病毒]]引发，该[[毒株|毒株]]与1946年-1957年间在世界上流行的H1N1毒株高度相似<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" />。此次大流行的基因分析结果以及其它异常特征，促使许多研究人员推测病毒的来源是实验室泄露事故或[[疫苗接種|疫苗接种]]事故<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":8">{{Cite journal|title=The 1977 H1N1 Influenza Virus Reemergence Demonstrated Gain-of-Function Hazards|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4611044/|last=Furmanski|first=Martin|date=2015-09-29|journal=mBio|issue=5|doi=10.1128/mBio.01434-15|volume=6|issn=2150-7511|pmc=4611044|pmid=26419881|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120180548/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4611044/}}</ref><ref name=":9">{{Cite journal|title=Historical Perspective — Emergence of Influenza A (H1N1) Viruses|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/abs/10.1056/NEJMra0904322|last=Zimmer|first=Shanta M.|last2=Burke|first2=Donald S.|date=2009-07-16|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.1056/NEJMra0904322|volume=361|pages=279–285|language=en|issn=0028-4793}}</ref><ref name=":13">{{Cite journal|title=Influenza: lessons from past pandemics, warnings from current incidents|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/nrmicro1208|last=Horimoto|first=Taisuke|last2=Kawaoka|first2=Yoshihiro|date=2005-08|journal=Nature Reviews Microbiology|issue=8|doi=10.1038/nrmicro1208|volume=3|pages=591–600|language=en|issn=1740-1534|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423191313/https://www.nature.com/articles/nrmicro1208}}</ref><ref name=":10">{{Cite web|title=Was H1N1 leaked from a laboratory?|url=https://blogs.bmj.com/bmj/2009/07/02/tom-nolan-was-h1n1-leaked-from-a-laboratory/|author=|date=2009-07-02|last=Nolan|first=Tom|format=|publisher=The BMJ|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616211557/http://blogs.bmj.com/bmj/2009/07/02/tom-nolan-was-h1n1-leaked-from-a-laboratory/|archivedate=2016-06-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 疫情历史 ==
1977年5月，[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]的北方地区包括[[辽宁省|辽宁]]、[[吉林省|吉林]]和[[天津市|天津]]等地爆发了[[流行性感冒|流感]]疫情<ref name=":12" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":4" />。中国的研究人员分离并确定了致病病毒为[[甲型流感病毒H1N1亞型|H1N1]]，但此次流感基本上只影响对H1N1病毒缺乏免疫力的中学生和小学生<ref name=":12" /><ref name=":2" />。临床症状相对轻微<ref name=":2" />。此后数月中，[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]其它地区以及[[英属香港|英属香港]]也受到影响<ref name=":12" /><ref name=":2" />。中国国家流感中心收集的1968年-1992年的监测报告显示，1977年[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]流感活动的强度仅次于1968年（[[1968年流感疫情|香港流感]]），高于其他年份<ref name=":12" />。

同年，在中国发生疫情后的短时间内，苏联的[[西伯利亚|西伯利亚]]也发现了H1N1感染，并迅速传遍苏联全境<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" />。苏联是第一个向[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]汇报疫情的国家（中华人民共和国于1981年才加入世卫组织<ref>{{Cite web|title=世界卫生组织驻华代表处|url=https://www.who.int/china/zh/about-us|publisher=世界卫生组织|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022053833/https://www.who.int/china/zh/about-us|archivedate=2019-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>），故此次大流行被称为“俄国流感”<ref name=":14">{{Cite web|title=1977 Russian Influenza - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/1977-russian-influenza|date=|publisher=[[ScienceDirect|ScienceDirect]]|language=en|access-date=2021-01-28|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130042642/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/1977-russian-influenza}}</ref>。

1977年，俄国流感蔓延至[[英国|英国]]<ref>{{Cite news|date=2013-01-25|title=The flu virus that nearly killed me|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-21125713|accessdate=2021-01-24|archivedate=2021-01-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118205028/https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-21125713|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1978年1月，[[美国|美国]]爆发疫情，最初在[[怀俄明州|怀俄明州]][[夏延_(怀俄明州)|夏延]]的一所高中内，患病率超过70%<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":5" /><ref name=":11">{{Cite news|author=Colen BD|date=1978-01-28|title=Russian Flu Has Arrived In the U.S.|language=en-US|work=《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/politics/1978/01/28/russian-flu-has-arrived-in-the-us/3d24b12b-5f75-480d-afc4-f31f1de81113/|issn=0190-8286|archivedate=2020-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716031837/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/politics/1978/01/28/russian-flu-has-arrived-in-the-us/3d24b12b-5f75-480d-afc4-f31f1de81113/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此后，美国多地的学校和军事基地内均有感染，但基本没有26岁以上的人患病，且死亡率较低<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":5" />。

1977年底，H1N1和[[H3N2|H3N2]]（[[1968年流感疫情|香港流感]]）开始在世界范围内同时流行，成为[[季节性流感|季节性流感]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":14" />。

== 病毒学 ==
[[H1N1|H1N1流感病毒]]有不同毒株，其中1950年代的[[毒株|毒株]]自1957年起便不在世界范围内流行，直至1977年重新出现<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":4" />。1977年的H1N1毒株与1950年代流行的毒株高度相似，但不完全一样<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" />。也有研究指出，1977年的病毒在被发现的约1年前就已经开始传播<ref name=":3" />。基于种种不寻常的特征，研究人员认为该毒株的起源系人为因素<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The biosecurity benefits of genetic engineering attribution|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-19149-2|last=Lewis|first=Gregory|last2=Jordan|first2=Jacob L.|date=2020-12-08|journal=Nature Communications|issue=1|doi=10.1038/s41467-020-19149-2|volume=11|pages=6294|language=en|issn=2041-1723|last3=Relman|first3=David A.|last4=Koblentz|first4=Gregory D.|last5=Leung|first5=Jade|last6=Dafoe|first6=Allan|last7=Nelson|first7=Cassidy|last8=Epstein|first8=Gerald L.|last9=Katz|first9=Rebecca|access-date=2021-07-22|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120074342/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-19149-2}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Centennial review of influenza in Taiwan|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6197989/|last=Gong|first=Yu-Nong|last2=Kuo|first2=Rei-Lin|date=2018-8|journal=Biomedical Journal|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.bj.2018.08.002|volume=41|pages=234–241|issn=2319-4170|pmc=6197989|pmid=30348266|last3=Chen|first3=Guang-Wu|last4=Shih|first4=Shin-Ru|access-date=2021-07-22|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119215733/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6197989/}}</ref>。起源理论包括：

* 普遍认为，1977年流行的H1N1毒株来源于实验室的泄露事故<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":8" /><ref name=":9" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":10" /><ref name=":14" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=New Strain May Edge Out Seasonal Flu Bugs|url=https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=103711274|date=2009-05-04|publisher=[[NPR|NPR]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809004621/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=103711274|archivedate=2020-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。病毒样本此前可能被冷藏于实验室内<ref name=":3" />，可能是从某个正在制备H1N1减活疫苗的实验室中泄露（此前曾有1976年美国猪流感疫情预警）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Threatened pandemics and laboratory escapes: Self-fulfilling prophecies|url=https://thebulletin.org/2014/03/threatened-pandemics-and-laboratory-escapes-self-fulfilling-prophecies/|access-date=2014-03-31|date=2014-03-31|last=Furmanski|first=Martin|website=Bulletin of the Atomic Scientists|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105123219/https://thebulletin.org/2014/03/threatened-pandemics-and-laboratory-escapes-self-fulfilling-prophecies/|archive-date=2019-01-05|url-status=live}}</ref>。但中国和苏联的科学家对此表示否认，称与此相关的实验室并未保存H1N1病毒或已经很久都未对其进行研究<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":122">{{Cite web|title=1977 H1N1 influenza virus is not relevant to the gain of function debate|url=https://www.virology.ws/2015/08/20/1977-h1n1-virus-not-relevant-to-gof-debate/|accessdate=|date=2015-08-20|publisher=Virology Blog|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124184625/https://www.virology.ws/2015/08/20/1977-h1n1-virus-not-relevant-to-gof-debate/|archivedate=2021-01-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Laboratory Escapes and "Self-fulfilling prophecy" Epidemics|url=https://armscontrolcenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Escaped-Viruses-final-2-17-14-copy.pdf|author=Furmanski M|date=2014-02-17|publisher=Center for Arms Control and Non-Proliferation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118120445/https://armscontrolcenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Escaped-Viruses-final-2-17-14-copy.pdf|archivedate=2020-11-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* 病毒来自于中国或苏联的[[疫苗接種|疫苗接种]]事故<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":122" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Influenza: old and new threats|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/nm1141|last=Palese|first=Peter|date=2004-12|journal=Nature Medicine|issue=12|doi=10.1038/nm1141|volume=10|pages=S82–S87|language=en|issn=1546-170X|access-date=2021-07-22|archive-date=2021-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624002938/https://www.nature.com/articles/nm1141}}</ref>。由于疫情在多地爆发，故有研究人员认为疫苗接种事故比单一实验室起源说可能性更大<ref name=":4" />。
* 病毒是苏联科学家制造的[[生化武器|生化武器]]，但可能性低<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":122" />。

== 临床数据 ==
此次俄国流感的[[病死率|病死率]]相对较低。1977年，[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]的研究人员发现不同学生群体的患病率不一，且有许多轻微和[[无症状|无症状]]感染<ref name=":2" />。在美国，有研究人员估计每10万人口中约有5人死亡（普通季节性流感则为6人）<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Trends in Recorded Influenza Mortality: United States, 1900–2004|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2374803/|last=Doshi|first=Peter|date=2008-5|journal=American Journal of Public Health|issue=5|doi=10.2105/AJPH.2007.119933|volume=98|pages=939–945|issn=0090-0036|pmc=2374803|pmid=18381993|access-date=2021-07-23|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224164051/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2374803//}}</ref>。

大部分受感染的人都不超过25岁或26岁<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":12" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":5" />。据估计，全球范围内共有70万人死于此次俄国流感<ref name=":6" /><ref name=":15" /><ref name=":7" />。

